02:23.533 --> 02:25.579
Somebody stop them!

02:25.613 --> 02:26.220
Please!

02:26.253 --> 02:28.171
My Lady, what's happened?

02:29.613 --> 02:31.244
Where is Rosaline?

02:31.278 --> 02:32.907
She's been kidnapped...

02:32.941 --> 02:34.554
by that Montague.

02:37.965 --> 02:41.579
Help! Help! Somebody help!

02:43.360 --> 02:47.423
Synced & corrected by -robtor-
